snippet.title: Disney Responds To Scarlett Johansson's Lawsuit
snippet.description:
A Walt Disney Company spokesperson responds after Scarlet Johansson filed a lawsuit for breach of contract over the release of "Black Widow". Plus, Marvel Studios president Kevin Feige is reportedly “angry and embarrassed” over the rift. Carlos Bustamante, Sangita Patel and guest co-host Liem Vu react on ET Canada Live.
